imdb.plot outline: Follows a 16 year old teenager named Carlos Masahi who witnessed his parents horrifying murder 6 years ago, he seeks revenge on the organization that killed his parents. Carlos forms a team with the one of the strongest people in the Island of Tokyo but before he goes to fight the organization he wanted to recruit one more ally named Cruz Avery, it would have been easy except Cruz said he will join there team only if Carlos wins a fight against him. Normally this would be easy for Carlos but once Cruz finds out the opponent is stronger, he gets really pissed and will go as far to brutally killing the opponent.
